# Example only — copy to `.npmrc` and fill in your own token from
# https://www.npmjs.com/settings/<user>/tokens
#
# Pick "Fine-grained" + "Read and publish" limited to scope `@crisxie/mbridge`.
# Do NOT commit your real `.npmrc`; it is in `.gitignore`.
#
;registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
